       I hd t rcntly wth  Zn prst, Ssn
       <span class="caps">
        O’C
       </span>
       nnll, wh s Vc Prsdnt f th
       <a href="http://www.sfzc.org/">
        Sn Frncsc Zn Cntr
       </a>
       . Sh’s  lvly prsn.
      </p>
      <p>
       On thng sh tlkd bt ws th “frms” tht r  bg prt f Zn mdttn — frms r th strct rls f pstr, hnd pss, sttng, nd thr prts f th mdttn tht r prscrbd by trdtn. Sm ppl cm t th zzn mdttn sssns bcs thy lk th frms, nd thrs cm n spt f th frms.
      </p>
      <p>
       Ethr wy, ppl mst fgr t thr rltn t ths frms. And thy mst dl wth tht n sm wy.
      </p>
      <p>
       I tld hr tht th lmts I st fr myslf hv th sm fnctn: lmtng myslf t
       <a href="http://mnmlist.com/50-things/">
        50 prsnl thngs
       </a>
       , r 5 sntnc mls, r 3 Mst Imprtnt Tsks ch dy, fr xmpl.
      </p>
      <p>
       Sm ppl mbrc ths lmts. Othr mnmlsts rjct thm bcs thy’r t rbtrrly rstrctng, r thy’r nt th pnt f mnmlsm.
      </p>
      <p>
       Ethr wy, y mst fgr t yr rltn t th lmts.
      </p>
      <p>
       Lmts r nt th pnt f mnmlsm, bt thy ccmplsh smthng mprtnt: thy frc s t fgr t wht’s mprtnt. And f w dn’t wnt t fgr t wht’s mprtnt, thy frc s t fgr t why.
      </p>
      <p>
       Thr’s  Zn stry (I’m prphrsng hr) bt  stdnt wh skd  tchr, “Wht’s th mst mprtnt thng?” And th tchr rpld, “Th mst mprtnt thng s skng wht’s th mst mprtnt thng.”
